Comment: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:40.05,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:100058,100058}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.67,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:108770,109670}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:54.12,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:109670,114120}You wagered the construction of the new gym on whether or not we win against the Soviet Union?{NOTE:バレー部XXX体育館建設をソ連との試合にかかってるんですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:58.04,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:114120,118040}So if we don't win, there's no gym?{NOTE:と言うことは、ソ連に勝たなければ、体育館をXXXてことね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:58.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:118040,118860}That's right.{NOTE:え。そうなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:03.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:118860,123260}That's why we have to win no matter what.{NOTE:だからこうなったらあたしたち何が何でもソ連に勝たなければ成らないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.94,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:123260,124940}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:06.06,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{TIME:124940,126060}No matter what?{NOTE:何が何でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:127200,128170}Exactly.{NOTE:そうよ。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:128170,129470}So let's win.{NOTE:勝ちましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:131270,133930}Why are you girls so quiet all of the sudden?{NOTE:皆、どうしたの？黙ってしまって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:16.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:133930,136500}Where's the usual "Yeah! Let's do this!"?{NOTE:「よし、やろう」って言ってくれないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:21.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:136500,141720}Yeah, you all were so enthusiastic in front of professor Hongou earlier.{NOTE:そうよ。本郷先生からソ連との試合聞いた時、皆あんなに張り切ってなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:144560,148260}Don't tell me you girls lost your confidence?{NOTE:それとも、それとも皆ソ連に勝つ自身をなくしてしまったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:148260,149740}Come on, Kakko.{NOTE:ね、カッコ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:149740,150760}What about you?{NOTE:あなたはどうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.52,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:150760,153520}Well, I'm confident.{NOTE:そ、それはあたしだって自身があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.42,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:153520,154420}But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:154420,155610}But what?{NOTE:でもなんなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.93,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:155610,159930}But saying that we have to win no matter is a bit much.{NOTE:ん、でもさ、「何が何でも絶対に勝つ」なんて、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:46.35,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:159930,166350}And I doubt prof. Hongou left us as a part of his strategy like Hayakawa-san said he did.{NOTE:だって、本郷先生はコーチ降りたのは早川さんが言うように本当に作戦上のことかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.92,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:166350,169920}Do you really believe it, Hayakawa-san?{NOTE:ね、早川さん、あなたはそう言い切れる自身があって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.14,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:170790,172140}You girls don't, right?{NOTE:ないよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.33,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:172140,173330}No way. Nope.{NOTE:ない、ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.92,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:173330,176920}Our opponent is the Soviet Union. Even the\hhigh schools couldn't beat them.{NOTE:XXX相手は日本の高校チームが構わない、ソ連チームだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:02.54,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:176920,182540}No matter how confident we are, we have a\hright to be worried without professor Hongou.{NOTE:そうよ。いくら自身があっても、毎日本郷先生のコーチがなって、やっぱり少し不安な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.02,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:183160,184020}Yep.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.70,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:184020,186700}Just think about the All-Japan tournament.{NOTE:今度の全国大会の優勝がいい見本よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.62,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:186700,188620}We don't stand a chance without professor Hongou.{NOTE:本郷先生はいなきゃ、やっぱりむりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.18,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:188620,191180}There's no way to know if we can win by ourselves.{NOTE:あたしたちだけじゃ絶対勝てるて言い切らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.85,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:191180,192850}No matter how much confidence we have. Right?{NOTE:いくら自身があっても。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:13.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:192850,193290}Yep.{NOTE:ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:193290,194180}This is bad.{NOTE:行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.40,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:194180,196400}I feared it would come to this.{NOTE:恐れていた時代成ってしまったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:196400,199120}Girls, aren't you forgetting something?{NOTE:皆、何か勘違いしてるんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:199120,201920}Fujimi Academy's volleyball club is the best in Japan.{NOTE:富士見学園バレー部は日本一なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:205960,207430}So what if they're the Soviet Union?{NOTE:ソ連が何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:32.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:207430,212040}If our seniors can beat them, then why can't we do the same?{NOTE:あたしたちの先輩はソ連に勝てるように、あたしたちだって勝てないわけがないじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:212040,215390}As long as I believe in myself, I won't lose.{NOTE:その自身があるかぎり、あたしは絶対に負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:38.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:215390,218010}Or, to put it better… I will win!{NOTE:いえ、勝てると言う確信があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.28,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:218010,220280}Yep. I think we can win too.{NOTE:あたしも勝てると思うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.41,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:220280,221410}– Really?\N– Yep.{NOTE:—そう？\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:222120,224930}I watched the last Soviet Union's game on the TV.{NOTE:この間もテレビのソ連の試合振りを見て思ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:224930,226600}Because of that, I'm sure we can win.{NOTE:あたしたちは勝てるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:50.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:226600,230180}No. There's no way Fujimi Academy can lose to the Soviet Union.{NOTE:いいえ。ソ連を倒すのはわが富士見学園バレー部以外にはないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.98,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:255730,256980}Let's do this, girls.{NOTE:やりましょう、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.57,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:256980,258570}– Yep. – All right.\N– Let's do this.{NOTE:—うん。—うん。\\N—やろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.89,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:258570,259890}– Yeah, yeah.\N– All right.{NOTE:—やろうやろう。ね？\\N—やるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.43,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:259890,262430}– Let's do our best.\N– Right.{NOTE:—XXX。—皆、頑張れね。—そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:262430,264540}Let's practice the spike. Assume positions.{NOTE:さ、千本スパイクよ。位置について。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.56,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:264540,265560}Okay!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.01,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:270120,271010}– Here I go.\N– OK.{NOTE:—行くわよ。\\N—OK。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.36,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:271010,272360}All right!{NOTE:XXX。それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.63,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:273230,274630}Come on, come on, come on.\NWhatcha doing?{NOTE:ほらほらほら、何やってんだ？}
