Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.80,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:290450,291800}I won't lose.{NOTE:負けるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:291800,294060}Naka, we won't beat the Soviets like this.{NOTE:ナカ、そんなことじゃソ連に勝てないわよ。}
